name: GI-learning
body:
### GI-LEARNING LIBRARY

`GI-LEARNING LIBRARY` is a C++ framework for [grammatical inference](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Grammar_induction).

Grammar induction algorithms:
- RPNI
- EDSM
- Blue*
- L*

Enjoy!
